文件中收集的情报相结合，从而构建出更完整的隧道网络图景。 还有美国和以色列官员认为，辛瓦尔很久以前就放弃了电子通信。据信，辛瓦尔可能通过信使网络与他领导的组织保持联系，该系统如何运作仍然是一个谜。 《纽约时报》形容称，辛瓦尔“像是一个鬼魂”，很少公开露面或者对追随者发布信息。这一次，他再次逃离了美以两国的追捕，行踪依旧成谜。身着女装混入人群，哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔如何躲过美以追杀？_加沙_地道_情报"},"attached_info":"CkAI6bf3k9XTuOdWEAMaCTExMDE3NDM3OSD237u2BjAAONIBQAxyCTY2NTUzNjE5OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"57 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fc99641f0df7166b4488e47e27e98baa_r.jpg?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"13_1725088600.882155","card_id":"Q_665620828","target":{"id":665620828,"title":"打《黑神话：悟空》总是不舍得吃药，总想贪最大化收益和省药是什么心理？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665620828","type":"question","created":1724921100,"answer_count":79,"follower_count":128,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,404,1172,169634,601256],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"葫芦想最大化收益，药想省，毕竟用一个少一个。。。"},"attached_info":"CkAI6bf3k9XTuOdWEAMaCTExMDE5MzIwOSCM6sC2BjAAOIABQA1yCTY2NTYyMDgyOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"56 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a0928a19e7072e9cde88fb0824b0adb9_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"14_1725088600.882819","card_id":"Q_664397817","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":664397817,"title":"教师节给之前的老师发祝福，老师会烦吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/664397817","type":"question","created":1723739502,"answer_count":119,"follower_count":136,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":